screen_name: Tired of seeing these tweets being liked on my timeline. The designated corona unit in my hospital is already 60% full. And a third of that population are on ventilators. The medical staff is not protected due to the lack of PPE. & this is ALL DURING QUARANTINE. https://t.co/m1eOsAGlir

My symptoms: 
- persistent fever 100-102 for 3 days 
- extreme eye pain & pounding headaches 
- muscle, and joint pain all around the body. It hurt to move. Worse on surgical sites and existing injuries
- tachypnea (rapid breathing) 
- Nausea, night sweats, no appetite
